g.text: Please explain the interesting point based on the three pictures.

The third image reveals some peculiar tanned circles on a mens feet, perfectly aligned with the holes in the sandals shown in the second image. It might be associated with his long-time outdoor activities since the first image indicates that the sun is intense. Therefore, the amusing sunburn occurs when the mens feet are exposed to prolonged sunlight. Due to the sandals partially blocking the UV rays, the skin away from the holes remains untanned while the skin under the holes gets tanned. However, the sunlight still reaches the skin between the holes, resulting in the tanned circles.

The set of images is a creative advertisement for animal adoption, which encourages people to take a note with contact information that also serves as a cage bar for the animals behind it. As people take the notes, animals are more likely to be adopted and freed from their cages.
What do these four pictures want to convey to us?
What changes have occurred to this wall in the pictures over time, and what does this set of pictures hope to show us through these changes?

This set of pictures mainly shows the change of a wall. In the beginning, the wall is a metal wall with only one line of writing, which has a silver shine and is very clean. In the third picture, some rust marks appear on the wall. A man stops by and stares at the wall. In the third image, there are some cars and a rusted wall with the outline of a knife. The last picture is already a rusted wall and the outline of an unrustedknife. It demonstrates the stable quality of the knife by showing that it will not rust after a long time.
What is the connection between these two pictures?

The first image is a gray T-shirt with Muggle text printed on it, while the second image is Google's logo. The connection between these two images is that their font and color scheme are very similar.
What makes this set of pictures look interesting?

Because the word 'muggle' uses the same font and color scheme as Google's logo, and their pronunciation is very similar. Its humor lies in using a homophonic stem and making the person wearing this dress look like a muggle.
What is this in picture?

This is an image of a fish. The fish is black and silvery, with a small mouth and eyes. It is lying on its side, with its tail and fins visible. The fish is about 5.51 inches long and 12.20 inches wide.
Is it still the fish you thought it was now?

No, I don't think it's a fish now, there are many colored pens and a fish-like case in this picture, these pens should be packed in a pencil case, so this should be a black and white fish-looking pencil case.
What else can this pencil case be used for besides holding pens?
It can also be used to hold stickers, erasers, or other stationery, but its fish-shaped appearance is too deceptive!
What is it and how to use it

This is an image of a camera lens. It is a type of camera lens that is designed to capture images and videos. It is typically used in combination with a camera body to form a camera system. The lens is designed to focus light onto a film or digital sensor, which captures the image.
Are you sure this is an image of a camera lens?
Im sorry. The image shows a large silver cup with a handle, featuring a lens-like design. The cup is made of stainless steel and there is also a spoon resting inside the cup.
Can this lens take photos?
No, it's just designed to look like a camera lens, but it's not a real camera lens.
